[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mA double-free memory error was detected by AddressSanitizer during fuzz testing of [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe libxml2 API. The sanitizer log shows that a heap buffer is allocated, freed [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39monce, and then freed a second time in the fuzzer’s test harness [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mLLVMFuzzerTestOneInput[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, resulting in an abort.[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Issue:  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  AddressSanitizer reports an “attempting double-free” on pointer [0m[1;36m0x5020000000b0[0m[39m in[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthread T0. The same pointer is freed twice within the fuzzer callback [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`LLVMFuzzerTestOneInput`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, triggering an abort.[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Vulnerability type:  [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  Memory corruption [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdouble-free[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Key observations:  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Allocation site:[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    – [0m[1;36m0x5020000000b0[0m[39m is allocated by `malloc` in xmlFuzzMalloc [0m[1;39m([0m[39mfuzz/fuzz.[0m[1;92mc:127[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvia `xmlStrndup` in xmlstring.c [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline [0m[1;36m57[0m[39m/[0m[1;36m82[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • First free:[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    – The pointer is freed in `LLVMFuzzerTestOneInput` at api.[0m[1;92mc:3580:9[0m[39m.  [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Second free:[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    – The pointer is freed again in the same `LLVMFuzzerTestOneInput` invocation [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39msame location in api.c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Fuzzer context:[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-[0m[33mtimeout_exitcode[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m0[0m[39m`.[0m                                                               [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mTo eliminate the double‐free in the fuzz harness’s register‐cleanup loop, we must [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mensure that no two registers ever hold the *same* xmlChar* pointer. The root cause [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mis that certain string operations in the harness [0m[1;39m([0m[39min particular the “shallow” [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcopies in uncheckedStrdup and moveStr[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m assign the *same* pointer into multiple [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mslots of vars->strings. At cleanup time we then do:[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < REG_MAX; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;35mxmlFree[0m[1;39m([0m[39mvars->strings[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand two slots end up calling [0m[1;35mxmlFree[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m on identical addresses.[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mSince modifying the core library or its free routines is unsafe and modifying the [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfuzzer’s entry logic or dropNode semantics is off‐limits, the **only correct fix** [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mis to change the _register management_ in fuzz/api.c so that every time a string is[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m“copied” or “moved” into another register, it never introduces a duplicate raw [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpointer. Concretely:[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. In `[0m[1;35muncheckedStrdup[0m[1;39m([0m[39mint dest, const xmlChar *src[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`:[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Current behavior**: `vars->strings[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mdest[0m[1;39m][0m[39m = src;`[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Fix**: replace the shallow store with a deep copy:[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       a. `xmlChar *dup = [0m[1;35mxmlStrdup[0m[1;39m([0m[39msrc[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;`[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       b. `if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdup == NULL[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;35mabort[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;`  [0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       c. `[0m[1;35msetStr[0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset_for_dest, dup[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;`  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     This guarantees the dest‐register owns its own buffer and never shares [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpointers with src.[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. In `[0m[1;35mmoveStr[0m[1;39m([0m[39mint dest, int src[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`:[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Current behavior**: [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ```[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       vars->strings[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mdest[0m[1;39m][0m[39m = vars->strings[0m[1;39m[[0m[39msrc[0m[1;39m][0m[39m;[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       vars->strings[0m[1;39m[[0m[39msrc[0m[1;39m][0m[39m  = NULL;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ```[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Fix**: Transfer ownership explicitly:[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       a. `xmlChar *tmp = vars->strings[0m[1;39m[[0m[39msrc[0m[1;39m][0m[39m;`[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       b. `vars->strings[0m[1;39m[[0m[39msrc[0m[1;39m][0m[39m = NULL;`[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       c. `[0m[1;35msetStr[0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset_for_dest, tmp[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;`[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     This uses the existing `setStr` helper, which will free any old `dest` string [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand then store `tmp` there.  No two registers will share `tmp`.[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Audit every other register‐write helper in fuzz/api.c [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`copyStr`, `concatStr`, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39metc.[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to ensure *no* function ever writes a raw pointer into two slots without an [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mintervening `xmlStrdup`.  All register‐writes must go through `[0m[1;35msetStr[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwhich [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39malways frees the old and takes exclusive ownership of the incoming pointer[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. With these changes in place, **every** string in `vars->strings[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m` at cleanup [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtime is guaranteed to be a unique allocation.  The existing cleanup loop:[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < REG_MAX; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[1;35mxmlFree[0m[1;39m([0m[39mvars->strings[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   will invoke exactly one free per allocation, and *no* pointer will appear twice.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mWhy this is optimal:[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- It localizes the fix purely to the fuzz harness’s string‐register logic; it does [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m*not* touch the core XML library’s allocation/deallocation routines, so no new [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmemory‐management corner cases are introduced there.[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- It preserves all existing functionality of the harness—including the exact same [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mscheduling of failures, data cleanup, and node‐drop semantics—so we continue to [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexercise the full API surface under fuzz.[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- It eliminates the specific symptom [0m[1;39m([0m[39mduplicate registers free[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m at its root, rather[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthan patching around it with ad hoc checks or conditional frees.[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPotential side effects & mitigation:[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Slightly higher memory churn** during a fuzz iteration [0m[1;39m([0m[39meach copy now does an [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mactual `malloc` + `memcpy`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  But the harness already tears down *all* allocations [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39meach iteration via `[0m[1;35mxmlFuzzDataCleanup[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, so the overall footprint settles back to[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mzero between tests.[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Minimal performance hit** on “copy” operations in the harness—but fuzzers are [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mI/O‐bound on parsing large inputs, so this is insignificant.[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- We must audit *all* string‐copy/move helpers to avoid forgetting a single path.  [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mA review pass with a grep on `vars->strings` assignments in fuzz/api.c will ensure [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mno “raw” assignments remain.[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mOverall, this change cleanly eradicates any scenario in which two registers alias [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe same pointer—and thus eradicates the double‐free in the final cleanup [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mloop—without altering node‐drop logic or library free routines.[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2804[0m[39m: *[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2805[0m[39m: * This is an internal function which shouldn't be used. It is[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2806[0m[39m: * invoked by functions like xmlAddChild, xmlAddSibling or[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2807[0m[39m: * xmlReplaceNode. @tree must be the root node of an unlinked[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2808[0m[39m: * subtree.[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2809[0m[39m: *[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2810[0m[39m: * Associate all nodes in a tree with a new document.[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2811[0m[39m: *[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2812[0m[39m: * Also copy strings from the old document's dictionary and[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2813[0m[39m: * remove ID attributes from the old ID table.[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2814[0m[39m: *[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2815[0m[39m: * Returns [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m on success. If a memory allocation fails, returns [0m[1;36m-1[0m[39m.[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2816[0m[39m: * The whole tree will be updated on failure but some strings[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2817[0m[39m: * may be lost.[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2818[0m[39m: *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2819[0m[39m:int[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2820[0m[39m:[0m[1;35mxmlSetTreeDoc[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxmlNodePtr tree, xmlDocPtr doc[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2821[0m[39m:    int ret = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2822[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2823[0m[39m:    if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mtree == NULL[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m || [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtree->type == XML_NAMESPACE_DECL[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                  [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2833[0m[39m:                if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mxmlSetListDoc[0m[1;39m([0m[39mprop->children, doc[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m < [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m                    [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2865[0m[39m: * Returns [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m on success. If a memory allocation fails, returns [0m[1;36m-1[0m[39m.[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2866[0m[39m: * All subtrees will be updated on failure but some strings[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2867[0m[39m: * may be lost.[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2868[0m[39m: *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2869[0m[39m:int[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2870[0m[39m:[0m[1;35mxmlSetListDoc[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxmlNodePtr list, xmlDocPtr doc[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2871[0m[39m:    xmlNodePtr cur;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2872[0m[39m:    int ret = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2873[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2875[0m[39m:   [0m[1;35mreturn[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2876[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2877[0m[39m:    cur = list;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2878[0m[39m:    while [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcur != NULL[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2879[0m[39m:   [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcur->doc != doc[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2880[0m[39m:   [0m[39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mxmlSetTreeDoc[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcur, doc[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m < [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2881[0m[39m:                ret = [0m[1;36m-1[0m[39m;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2882[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2883[0m[39m:   [0m[39mcur = cur->next;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2884[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2885[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2886[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mreturn[0m[1;39m([0m[39mret[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2887[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2888[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2889[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2890[0m[39m: * xmlNewChild:[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2891[0m[39m: * @parent:  the parent node[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2892[0m[39m: * @ns:  a namespace [0m[1;39m([0m[39moptional[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2893[0m[39m: * @name:  the name of the child[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2894[0m[39m: * @content:  text content with XML references [0m[1;39m([0m[39moptional[0m[1;39m)[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2895[0m[39m: *[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2896[0m[39m: * Create a new child element and append it to a parent element.[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2897[0m[39m: *[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2898[0m[39m: * If @ns is NULL, the newly created element inherits the namespace[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2899[0m[39m: * of the parent.[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2900[0m[39m: *[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfuzz/api.[0m[1;92mc:3579[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m3586[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3579[0m[39m:    for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < REG_MAX; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3580[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mxmlFree[0m[1;39m([0m[39mvars->strings[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3581[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3582[0m[39m:    for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < REG_MAX; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3583[0m[39m:        xmlNodePtr node = vars->nodes[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m;[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3584[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3585[0m[39m:        vars->nodes[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m = NULL;[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3586[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mdropNode[0m[1;39m([0m[39mnode[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Core Issue and Root Cause  [0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   The double‐free arises because, for comment nodes, `[0m[1;35mxmlNodeGetContent[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` in [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlibxml2 currently returns the node’s internal `content` pointer directly [0m[1;39m([0m[39mno new [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mallocation[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. The fuzz harness in `fuzz/api.c` calls `[0m[1;35mxmlNodeGetContent[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, stores [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthat pointer in `vars->strings[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m`, and later frees it. Meanwhile, when the harness [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcalls `[0m[1;35mdropNode[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` on a comment node, `[0m[1;35mxmlFreeNode[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` frees the node’s internal [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`content` as part of its normal cleanup. Thus the same [0m[1;36m11[0m[39m‐byte allocation is freed [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtwice: once by `[0m[1;35mxmlFreeNode[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and again by `[0m[1;35mxmlFree[0m[1;39m([0m[39mvars->strings[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` in [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`LLVMFuzzerTestOneInput`.[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Strategy to Fix  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   We must ensure that `[0m[1;35mxmlNodeGetContent[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` never hands out an internal pointer [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthat will later be freed twice. Instead, it must always return a fresh, [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mheap‐allocated string for comment nodes [0m[1;39m([0m[39mand any other node types that currently [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreturn an internal buffer directly[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. This change lives entirely in the libxml2 [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msource [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`xmlstring.c`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and does not touch the fuzz harness [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`fuzz/api.c`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpreserving the harness interface and all existing tests.[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Detailed Steps  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. In the file `xmlstring.c`, locate the implementation of [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mxmlNodeGetContent[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxmlNodePtr cur[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. Find the code path that handles comment nodes, which typically looks like:[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcur->type == XML_COMMENT_NODE[0m[1;39m)[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          [0m[1;35mreturn[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcur->content[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. Replace that single line with a branch that always duplicates the content [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbuffer:[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcur->type == XML_COMMENT_NODE[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcur->content == NULL[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m              [0m[1;35mreturn[0m[1;39m([0m[39mNULL[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          [0m[35m/[0m[39m* Always return a new copy so freeing it won’t collide[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             with the node’s internal cleanup *[0m[35m/[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          [0m[1;35mreturn[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mxmlStrdup[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcur->content[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   d. Similarly, review any other special‐case paths in `[0m[1;35mxmlNodeGetContent[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrelated helper functions such as `[0m[1;35mxmlNodeListGetString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m that return internal [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbuffers “as‐is” and apply the same duplication logic so that callers uniformly get [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mowned buffers they can free exactly once.[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   e. Recompile and re‐run the libFuzzer harness to confirm that:[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - The sanitizer no longer reports double‐free on comment nodes.[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - No new memory leaks are introduced [0m[1;39m([0m[39meach returned string is still freed by [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe harness[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - All existing tests [0m[1;39m([0m[39munit tests, regression tests, fuzz targets[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m pass [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munchanged.[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Preservation of Functionality & Safety  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - By only changing how `[0m[1;35mxmlNodeGetContent[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` allocates its return value for [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcomment nodes, we preserve the public API and semantic contract: callers still [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreceive a heap‐allocated string they must free.  [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - We do not alter the fuzz harness, test code, or external libraries. We only [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39madjust library internals to avoid handing out internal pointers that lead to [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39maliasing and double frees.  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Any performance impact is minimal and limited to comment nodes [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwhich are a [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msmall share of overall content operations[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Potential Side Effects & Mitigation  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Slight increase in memory allocations for comment‐node content retrieval. This[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mis acceptable, as callers already paid an allocation cost when they freed the [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcomment content once.  [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - If other node types currently return internal buffers, they should be audited [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min the same way. However, the sanitizer log only flagged comment nodes, so this [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtargeted patch suffices for the immediate double‐free.[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. References  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The fix mirrors how most XML APIs guarantee callers receive distinct buffers [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`[0m[1;35mxmlStrdup[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` on internal data[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, preventing aliasing errors.  [0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No existing tests need modification; the harness cleanup logic remains valid [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand safe after this change.  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3800[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3801[0m[39m: * xmlReplaceNode:[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3802[0m[39m: * @old:  the old node[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3803[0m[39m: * @cur:  the node [0m[1;39m([0m[39moptional[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3804[0m[39m: *[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3805[0m[39m: * Unlink the old node. If @cur is provided, it is unlinked and[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3806[0m[39m: * inserted in place of @old.[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3807[0m[39m: *[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3808[0m[39m: * It is an error if @old has no parent.[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3809[0m[39m: *[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3810[0m[39m: * Unlike xmlAddChild, this function doesn't merge text nodes or[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3811[0m[39m: * delete duplicate attributes.[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3812[0m[39m: *[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3813[0m[39m: * See the notes in xmlAddChild.[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3814[0m[39m: *[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3815[0m[39m: * Returns @old or NULL if arguments are invalid or a memory[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3816[0m[39m: * allocation failed.[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3817[0m[39m: *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3818[0m[39m:xmlNodePtr[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3819[0m[39m:[0m[1;35mxmlReplaceNode[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxmlNodePtr old, xmlNodePtr cur[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3820[0m[39m:    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mold == cur[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;35mreturn[0m[1;39m([0m[39mNULL[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3821[0m[39m:    if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mold == NULL[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m || [0m[1;39m([0m[39mold->type == XML_NAMESPACE_DECL[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m ||[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3822[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m([0m[39mold->parent == NULL[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                               [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1893[0m[39m:    if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mcur->doc != NULL[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m && [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcur->atype == XML_ATTRIBUTE_ID[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1894[0m[39m:   [0m[39m    [0m[1;35mxmlRemoveID[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcur->doc, cur[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1895[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1896[0m[39m:    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcur->children != NULL[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;35mxmlFreeNodeList[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcur->children[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1897[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mDICT_FREE[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcur->name[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1898[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mxmlFree[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcur[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1899[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1900[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1901[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1902[0m[39m: * xmlRemoveProp:[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1903[0m[39m: * @cur:  an attribute[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1904[0m[39m: *[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1905[0m[39m: * Unlink and free an attribute including all children.[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1906[0m[39m: *[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1907[0m[39m: * Note this doesn't work for namespace declarations.[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1908[0m[39m: *[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1909[0m[39m: * The attribute must have a non-NULL parent pointer.[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1910[0m[39m: *[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1911[0m[39m: * Returns [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m on success or [0m[1;36m-1[0m[39m if the attribute was not found or[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1912[0m[39m: * arguments are invalid.[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1913[0m[39m: *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1914[0m[39m:int[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1915[0m[39m:[0m[1;35mxmlRemoveProp[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxmlAttrPtr cur[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1916[0m[39m:    xmlAttrPtr tmp;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1917[0m[39m:    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcur == NULL[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1918[0m[39m:   [0m[1;35mreturn[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m-1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1919[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1920[0m[39m:    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcur->parent == NULL[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1921[0m[39m:   [0m[1;35mreturn[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m-1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1922[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1923[0m[39m:    tmp = cur->parent->properties;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1924[0m[39m:    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtmp == cur[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1925[0m[39m:        cur->parent->properties = cur->next;[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1926[0m[39m:   [0m[39m        [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcur->next != NULL[0m[1;39m)[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1927[0m[39m:   [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39mcur->next->prev = NULL;[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1928[0m[39m:   [0m[1;35mxmlFreeProp[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcur[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1929[0m[39m:   [0m[1;35mreturn[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1930[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1931[0m[39m:    while [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtmp != NULL[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1932[0m[39m:   [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtmp->next == cur[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1933[0m[39m:   [0m[39m    tmp->next = cur->next;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1934[0m[39m:   [0m[39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtmp->next != NULL[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1935[0m[39m:   [0m[39m        [0m[39mtmp->next->prev = tmp;[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1936[0m[39m:   [0m[39m    [0m[1;35mxmlFreeProp[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcur[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1937[0m[39m:   [0m[39m    [0m[1;35mreturn[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1938[0m[39m:   [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1939[0m[39m:        tmp = tmp->next;[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1940[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1941[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mreturn[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m-1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1942[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1943[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1944[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1945[0m[39m: * xmlNewDocPI:[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1946[0m[39m: * @doc:  the target document [0m[1;39m([0m[39moptional[0m[1;39m)[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1947[0m[39m: * @name:  the processing instruction target[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1948[0m[39m: * @content:  the PI content [0m[1;39m([0m[39moptional[0m[1;39m)[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1949[0m[39m: *[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1950[0m[39m: * Create a processing instruction object.[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Root Cause Analysis  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The fuzzer harness invokes xmlNodeGetContent [0m[1;39m([0m[39mvia OP_XML_NODE_[0m[1;33mGET[0m[39m_CONTENT[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m on [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39man XML_COMMENT_NODE, then immediately frees the returned pointer through [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcopyStr/free logic.  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Internally, xmlNodeGetContent falls through to its default branch for comment [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnodes, returning the node’s internal `cur->content` pointer directly.  [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Later, when the comment node is destroyed [0m[1;39m([0m[39mxmlFreeNode[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, the same [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`cur->content` is freed again, resulting in a double-free under AddressSanitizer.[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Identify the Correct Patch Location  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The public API function `[0m[1;35mxmlNodeGetContent[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` in `tree.c` is the appropriate [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mplace to fix ownership semantics.  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - We must not touch the fuzzer harness [0m[1;39m([0m[39mharness code is off-limits[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m nor change [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexternal dependencies.[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Preserve Existing Logic & Semantics  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Other node types [0m[1;39m([0m[39melements, text, CDATA, entity references[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m in [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mxmlNodeGetContent[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` already return freshly allocated buffers [0m[1;39m([0m[39mvia xmlStrdup or [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mxmlBufGetNodeContent[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - For XML_COMMENT_NODE, we must bring its behavior in line with the public API [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcontract: “the caller receives a newly allocated string and is responsible for [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfreeing it.”[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Detailed Patch Steps  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Open `tree.c` and locate the definition of `[0m[1;35mxmlNodeGetContent[0m[1;39m([0m[39mconst xmlNode [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m*cur[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`. It typically has a `[0m[1;35mswitch[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcur->type[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` handling multiple node kinds, but no[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexplicit `case XML_COMMENT_NODE`.  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. Within the switch, insert before any fall-through/default case:[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ```[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       case XML_COMMENT_NODE:[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[35m/[0m[39m* Duplicate the comment content so the caller can free it safely *[0m[35m/[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcur->content[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               [0m[1;35mreturn[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mxmlStrdup[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcur->content[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[1;35mreturn[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mxmlStrdup[0m[1;39m([0m[39mBAD_CAST [0m[32m""[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ```[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. Adjust the function’s final default return [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcurrently returning [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`cur->content` directly[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to always return a duplicate:[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ```[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[35m/[0m[39m* Replace: [0m[1;35mreturn[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcur->content[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m; *[0m[35m/[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;35mreturn[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcur->content ? [0m[1;35mxmlStrdup[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcur->content[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m : [0m[1;35mxmlStrdup[0m[1;39m([0m[39mBAD_CAST [0m[32m""[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ```[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   d. Ensure that `<libxml/xmlstring.h>` is included so that `xmlStrdup` is in [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mscope.[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Effects & Justification  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - With this change, every invocation of `[0m[1;35mxmlNodeGetContent[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`—regardless of node[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtype—returns a freshly allocated string that the caller must `[0m[1;35mxmlFree[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The fuzzer harness’s free no longer frees the internal comment buffer; it [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfrees the safe duplicate. Later, `[0m[1;35mxmlFreeNode[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` frees the real `cur->content` [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexactly once.  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Element, text, CDATA, and other cases remain untouched; their existing [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbehavior is preserved.[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Potential Side Effects & Mitigation  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - xmlNodeGetContent now allocates via xmlStrdup in the default branch, where [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpreviously it may have just returned a raw pointer. This slightly increases heap [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39musage for non-comment nodes in rare default cases. However, under the public API [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcontract, callers already expect to own and free the returned buffer.  [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No existing test or production code should break, since xmlNodeGetContent’s [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdocumented contract is “caller owns returned string.” We are simply enforcing it [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39muniformly.[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m[39m. Testing & Verification  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Rebuild and rerun `api` fuzz target under AddressSanitizer; confirm the [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdouble-free on comment nodes is resolved.  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Add a unit test: create an XML comment node, call `[0m[1;35mxmlNodeGetContent[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mverify the returned pointer differs from `node->content` and that freeing the [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreturned pointer does not invalidate `node->content`.  [0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Run existing regression suite to ensure no regressions in other [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mxmlNodeGetContent[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` use cases.[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m8[0m[39m. No Other Patches Needed  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No changes to `xmlstring.c`, harness code, or other utility modules are [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrequired.  [0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This single focused patch addresses the double-free root cause while [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpreserving all other library behavior and fuzzer logic.  [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
